=Analyze these aim trainer stats for the player over the past week:
- Accuracy: {{ $json.accuracy }}%
- Reaction Times (last 20 shots): {{ $json.reactionTimes || "[215, 230, 195, 240]" }}
- Urgency Index (speed focus vs control): {{ $json.averageUrgencyIndex || 1.15 }}
- Over-Flick Coefficient (overshooting target): {{ $json.overFlickCoefficient || 1.08 }}
- Miss Quadrant Distribution: TL:{{ $json.missQuadrants?.topLeft }}%, TR:{{ $json.missQuadrants?.topRight }}%, BL:{{ $json.missQuadrants?.bottomLeft }}%, BR:{{ $json.missQuadrants?.bottomRight }}%

Provide 3 short, brutally honest tactical tips using competitive shooter terminology (e.g. Valorant/CS/Apex) on how they can fix their mechanical deficiencies this week.
